description:
&lt;p&gt;A exciting opportunity has come up in the Health Records Department. We are looking for someone to come and join our Health Records team as Senior Health Records Clerk. Working across four sites (GWP, Lister, QE2 and Hertford County) predominantly based at Lister you will be responsible for line management of Health Records Clerks completing appraisals, sickness meetings,121 conversations and ensuring the service which we provide meets the needs of our service users .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Knowledge of Lorenzo and iFit would be beneficial, cross site working may be required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Steve O&#39;keefe&lt;br /&gt;01438 286924&lt;/p&gt;
